  <brief_title>Effect of Genetic Polymorphisms on Platinum Based Chemotherapy in Non Small Cell Lung Cancer</brief_title>
  <official_title>Effect of Genetic Polymorphisms on Clinical Outcome of Platinum Based Chemotherapy in Non-Small Cell Lung Cancer Patients</official_title>
