  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      This Study evaluate the effect of Polymorphism in the Excision repair cross-complementing
      group 5 (ERCC5) (rs1047768 and rs751402) gene on the clinical outcome of Platinum-based
      regimens used in the treatment of Non-Small Cell Lung Cancer (NSCLC) patients
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
