    <measure>Progression-free survival (PFS)</measure>
    <time_frame>From the date of starting the chemotherapy until the date of documented disease progression or date of death from any cause assessed up to 12 months</time_frame>
    <description>It's defined as the time from day 1 of chemotherapy to the day of documented disease progression or death from any cause.</description>
